title: 04/13/2021 - DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 04/13/2021 - DPS Best Of
description:
Jason Smith and Jason McIntyre are in for Dan Patrick and the Danettes, reacting to Jamal Murray going down with a no contact leg injury against the Warriors who were celebrating Steph Curry passing Wilt Chamberlain for most points in franchise history. The guys agree Aaron Rodgers is waiting for his time to 'strike' and ask for a trade from the Packers. Plus, NBA Vet and Analyst Ryan Hollins joins the guys after news breaks that Murray suffered a torn ACL to talk about how the Nuggets can still salvage the season.
